336
00:17:23,976 --> 00:17:25,683
Newton Haven.
纽顿海文

337
00:17:26,445 --> 00:17:31,750
Take a moment to look upon it in its original colors, boys, for tonight we paint it red.
花点时间记住它原来的模样 兄弟们 今晚我们要给它改头换面了

338
00:17:36,956 --> 00:17:40,335
Oh, no, no, no. Shit.
噢 不要 不 不 不 糟糕

339
00:17:42,828 --> 00:17:45,363
Fuck, fuck, fuck.
妈的 妈的

340
00:17:45,364 --> 00:17:46,665
Fuck, fuck.
妈的

341
00:17:46,666 --> 00:17:48,800
Oh, no, it's okay, I did it all in the services.
噢 不 没事的 我常在服务区这么干

342
00:17:52,838 --> 00:17:54,476
Know why I pulled you over, sir?
知道我为什么拦你吗 先生?

343
00:17:55,641 --> 00:17:57,143
Was the music too loud?
音乐太吵吗?

344
00:17:57,276 --> 00:18:00,723
- Your left brake light is faulty.  - Oh!
- 你左侧刹车灯坏了  - 噢!

345
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:04,649
The old brake lights! So called because they're always breaking.
老掉牙的刹车灯! 难怪叫刹车灯 因为动不动就歇菜

346
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:05,993
I'll get that sorted out, Officer.
警官 我一定会修好的

347
00:18:06,686 --> 00:18:09,292
- Can I see your license, sir?  - Yup.
- 能给我看看你的驾照吗 先生?  - 好的

348
00:18:10,523 --> 00:18:11,690
Ah!
啊!

349
00:18:11,691 --> 00:18:13,158
You know what? It's in my wallet.
完蛋了? 在我钱包里

350
00:18:13,159 --> 00:18:15,994
And I left that at the bloody gym!
钱包落在健身房了!

351
00:18:15,995 --> 00:18:20,632
- Any other form of identification?  - No, it's all in my sports bag.
- 有什么其他证件吗?  - 没有 都在我包里

352
00:18:20,633 --> 00:18:23,201
That's bloody typical, isn't it? Um...
这种状况挺常见的 对吗? 嗯...

353
00:18:23,202 --> 00:18:26,304
I'll give you my name and address, you can run me through the old system.
我把名字和地址告诉你 你能在系统里查到

354
00:18:26,305 --> 00:18:27,340
Go on then.
说吧

355
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:29,474
It's Peter Page.
我叫皮特・佩奇

356
00:18:29,475 --> 00:18:34,356
48 Bishop's Gardens, London, N2 T12.
住在伦敦北区 48号 毕肖普花园

