相信我就是了

366
00:18:55,234 --> 00:18:58,036
So, Mr. Page, what brings you to Newton Haven?
那么 皮特先生 你为什么来纽顿海文?

367
00:18:58,037 --> 00:19:01,006
Well, we're all from here. We're just back to see the sights.
我们过去都住这 回来看看风景

368
00:19:01,007 --> 00:19:03,008
Have a crack at the old Golden Mile.
重温儿时回忆

369
00:19:03,009 --> 00:19:04,376
Might get a bit messy.
也许还会捣点乱

370
00:19:04,377 --> 00:19:06,544
Well, you make sure you get that brake light fixed
这么说吧 首先你得保证把刹车灯修好

371
00:19:06,545 --> 00:19:09,151
and you might want to do an emissions test, too.
可能还得做个尾气标准测试

372
00:19:09,882 --> 00:19:11,149
Oh, and, Peter.
噢 还有 皮特

373
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:12,390
Don't make too much mess.
记住别闹大了

374
00:19:14,587 --> 00:19:15,725
We won't!
不会的!

375
00:19:15,988 --> 00:19:17,023
Hmm.
嗯

376
00:19:17,123 --> 00:19:18,289
I don't understand.
我搞不懂

377
00:19:18,290 --> 00:19:20,225
It's simple, Pete.
很简单 皮特

378
00:19:20,226 --> 00:19:23,228
The car's still registered to you, it has been since 1989.
从1989年起 这辆车就一直在你名下

379
00:19:23,229 --> 00:19:24,663
But I've moved three times since then.
但那以后我都搬过三次家了

380
00:19:24,664 --> 00:19:26,231
I know, I changed the log book.
我知道 我改了记录

381
00:19:26,232 --> 00:19:28,033
Where do you think all those points came from?
不然我哪来分给警察扣?

382
00:19:28,034 --> 00:19:29,240
Jesus. You guys need to relax.
天啊 大伙都放松点

383
00:19:34,634 --> 00:19:36,840


384
00:19:45,851 --> 00:19:47,786
Do you know how much trouble you could get into?
你知道你会惹出一堆麻烦吗?

385
00:19:47,787 --> 00:19:49,454
Do you know how much trouble I'm already in?
你都不知道我已经一团糟了?

386
00:19:49,455 --> 00:19:50,689
What's that supposed to mean?
你这话什么意思?

387
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:54,025
Hey. What the hell is this? Why are we even here?
嘿 这究竟是怎么回事? 我们为什么来这里?

388
00:19:54,026 --> 00:19:56,628
We are here to get annihilated.
一起全军覆没

389
00:19:57,930 --> 00:19:59,931
Have you got any plans for dinner at all?
晚上有什么想吃的吗?

390
00:19:59,932 --> 00:20:02,867
Tonight, we will be partaking of a liquid repast
今天晚上 我们要完成豪饮马拉松

391
00:20:02,868 --> 00:20:05,236
as we wend our way up The Golden Mile.
今天晚上酒就是我们的晚餐

392
00:20:05,237 --> 00:20:08,006
Commencing with an inaugural tankard at The First Post,
先去一号邮局 来一大桶啤酒

393
00:20:08,007 --> 00:20:11,176
then onto The Old Familiar, The Famous Cock, The Cross Hands,
然后去老相识 闻名雄鸡 交叉之手

394
00:20:11,177 --> 00:20:12,644
The Good Companions, The Trusty Servant,
好伙伴 忠仆

395
00:20:12,645 --> 00:20:14,879
The Two Headed Dog, The Mermaid, The Beehive, The King's Head
双头猎狗 美人鱼 蜂窝 国王之颅

396
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,915
and The Hole in the Wall for a measure of the same.
然后墙洞 和上回路线一致

397
00:20:16,916 --> 00:20:20,785
All before the last bittersweet pint in that most fateful terminus,
直到宿命的终点站 喝光最后一滴酒

398
00:20:20,786 --> 00:20:22,053
The World's End.
世界的尽头

399
00:20:22,054 --> 00:20:23,121
Leave a light on, good lady,
为我们留盏灯 夫人

400
00:20:23,122 --> 00:20:25,523
for though we may return with a twinkle in our eyes,
虽然我们回来时 眼神还透着兴奋劲

401
00:20:25,524 --> 00:20:27,731
