但我敢打包票 全都烂醉如泥了

402
00:21:48,875 --> 00:21:49,276


403
00:21:49,875 --> 00:21:50,876
Come on!
来吧!

404
00:21:57,049 --> 00:21:58,850
- Until 1840...  - Fucking hell.
- 直到1840年...  - 去他妈的

405
00:21:58,851 --> 00:22:01,953
this building was the site of Newton Haven's first post office.
这里还是纽顿海文第一家邮局

406
00:22:01,954 --> 00:22:03,988
Until an enterprising business fellow decided that
一个进取的生意人发现

407
00:22:03,989 --> 00:22:07,025
far from befitting the sending and receiving of mail
相比用来收发邮件

408
00:22:07,026 --> 00:22:09,227
it was perhaps better suited as a humble taproom
这儿更适合做酒吧

409
00:22:09,228 --> 00:22:13,005
where a weary traveler might get matted. Come on.
给疲倦的旅人歇歇脚 快进来吧

410
00:22:14,834 --> 00:22:17,135
Ah!
啊!

411
00:22:17,136 --> 00:22:18,774
It's like déjà vu.
简直是昨日重现

412
00:22:24,910 --> 00:22:27,078
I don't remember this at all. Has it been refurbished?
我一点印象都没有 这里重装了吗?

413
00:22:27,079 --> 00:22:29,047
Been bought by a chain, hasn't it?
被连锁店收购了 对吗?

414
00:22:29,048 --> 00:22:30,715
Part of that nationwide initiative to rob
全国性提案的一部分

415
00:22:30,716 --> 00:22:33,629
small, charming pubs of any discernible character.
同化那些个性的小酒吧

416
00:22:33,752 --> 00:22:36,198
Starbucking, man. It's happening everywhere.
好比星巴克 哥们 这种事很常见

417
00:22:37,690 --> 00:22:39,290
Can't take away that smell, though.
不过 味道还和过去一样

418
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:40,959
I'm sure they tried.
我相信他们尽力了

419
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:44,863
- Good evening, Raymondo. The prodigal sons return.  - Eh?
- 晚上好 雷蒙多 浪子们回头了  - 什么?

420
00:22:44,864 --> 00:22:46,464
Who's on the guest list tonight?
今晚都有什么嘉宾?

421
00:22:46,465 --> 00:22:48,433
- Come again?  - The guest ales.
- 你说什么?  - 宾客名单

422
00:22:48,434 --> 00:22:51,269
We, sir, are doing The Golden Mile and you have
我们几个 先生 我们来重温美好时光了

423
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:53,443
the honor of drawing first blood.
你有幸成为第一位见证者

424
00:22:53,606 --> 00:22:56,177
- What do you recommend?  - There's one. Crowning Glory.
- 有什么推荐的?  - 有一个还不错 至高荣耀

425
00:22:57,209 --> 00:22:58,711
- Rather fitting.  - How's that?
- 再合适不过了  - 怎么说?

426
00:22:58,811 --> 00:23:00,612
- I'm Gary King.  - What?
- 我叫加里・金  - 什么?

427
00:23:00,613 --> 00:23:02,914
- So tell me more.  - About what?
- 多说点  - 关于什么?

428
00:23:02,915 --> 00:23:05,250
Crowning Glory. Is it nutty? Is it foamy? Is it happy?
至高荣耀 带果仁吗? 气泡多吗? 会让人开心吗?

429
00:23:05,251 --> 00:23:07,986
Does it have a surprisingly fruity note which lingers on the tongue?
是不是有种特殊的果味 会留香唇齿间?

430
00:23:07,987 --> 00:23:10,321
- Hmm. It's beer.  - Hmm.
- 嗯 啤酒而已  - 好吧

431
00:23:10,322 --> 00:23:11,723
We'll have five of those, please.
我们要五杯

432
00:23:11,724 --> 00:23:14,728
No. Sorry. Can we have four of those and a tap water, please?
不 不好意思 只要四杯外加杯水 谢谢

433
00:23:15,194 --> 00:23:16,400
What?
什么?

434
00:23:25,371 --> 00:23:27,405
I don't believe this,
不敢相信

435
00:23:27,406 --> 00:23:32,082
a man of your legendary prowess drinking fucking rain.
猛男居然喝白开水

436
00:23:32,878 --> 00:23:34,879
