01:00:51,882 --> 01:00:53,215
Any way they like.
用他们想用的任何方式

1113
01:00:53,216 --> 01:00:59,064
Blood tests, the nit nurse, sweat, kissing, saliva on the rim of a glass.
血液检测 打针护士 汗液 亲吻 杯缘的唾液

1114
01:00:59,689 --> 01:01:02,358
Why do you think I drink with this crazy straw?
不然我为什么要用这么奇怪的吸管喝酒?

1115
01:01:02,359 --> 01:01:03,736
Not so crazy now, is it?
现在看上去不那么奇怪了吧?

1116
01:01:03,994 --> 01:01:06,975
If you're not on their side, they'll create a version that is.
如果你反对他们 他们就会创造一个同意他们的你

1117
01:01:07,397 --> 01:01:11,277
They can bring you back exactly the same or even make you young again.
他们可以复制一模一样的你 甚至创造更年轻的你

1118
01:01:11,768 --> 01:01:13,702
It looks like you, it even has your memories,
那看上去很像你 甚至还有你的记忆

1119
01:01:13,703 --> 01:01:16,238
but really it's just a vessel to spread their message.
但事实上那只是传播他们信息的管道

1120
01:01:16,239 --> 01:01:20,609
Trust, love, respect, desire.
信任 爱 尊敬 欲望

1121
01:01:20,610 --> 01:01:23,352
Replaced in the name of progress.
都以进化的名义被取代了

1122
01:01:24,614 --> 01:01:26,992
So, what happens to the people who get replaced?
那么 那些被替代的人怎么样了?

1123
01:01:27,117 --> 01:01:30,186
The empties? Don't ask me what happens to them.
废容器? 别问我他们怎么样了

1124
01:01:30,187 --> 01:01:31,554
Why, what happens to the empties?
为什么 废容器怎么样了?

1125
01:01:31,555 --> 01:01:33,255
I told you not to ask me that!
我告诉过你不要问我!

1126
01:01:33,256 --> 01:01:35,532
Go! Get out, before it's too late!
快走! 快离开这里 否则就太晚了!

1127
01:01:39,629 --> 01:01:41,631
- Basil?  - I said go!
- 巴希尔?  - 我说过快走!

1128
01:01:45,669 --> 01:01:47,114
This just can't be good.
这太不好了

1129
01:01:47,437 --> 01:01:50,350
Sam, who was the boy that you liked in sixth form? Adrian?
山姆 你高二高三的时候喜欢的男孩子是谁? 阿德里安?

1130
01:01:51,174 --> 01:01:53,654
Adrian Keane. Why?
阿德里安・基恩 怎么了?

1131
01:01:54,277 --> 01:01:55,483
He's over there.
他在那里

1132
01:02:04,521 --> 01:02:07,161
Hey, Sam. How's life?
嘿 山姆 过得怎么样?

1133
01:02:11,528 --> 01:02:13,629
- Sam, we have to get out of here!  - We have to get out of here!
- 山姆 我们得离开这里!  - 我们得离开这里!

1134
01:02:13,630 --> 01:02:15,803
- Where are the others?  - They're blending in.
- 其他人在哪里?  - 他们在调情

1135
01:02:17,601 --> 01:02:19,239
Oh, fuck!
他妈的!

1136
01:02:21,638 --> 01:02:23,481
- Gary!  - Oh. No, just one more song.
- 加里!  - 不要 再来一首歌

1137
01:02:23,873 --> 01:02:25,874
Gary, she's a blank!
加里 她是空白人!

1138
01:02:25,875 --> 01:02:27,309
Don't be so judgmental.
别这么歧视

1139
01:02:27,310 --> 01:02:28,311
Oh, for fuck...
他妈的...

1140
01:02:29,100 --> 01:02:30,200
学校联谊会

1141
01:02:30,680 --> 01:02:31,681
Oh, yeah. Come on.
好吧 走吧

1142
01:02:31,881 --> 01:02:33,292
Still got it. Enough's enough.
还是到手了 够了就是够了

1143
01:02:33,550 --> 01:02:34,683
Let's go.
我们快走

1144
01:02:34,684 --> 01:02:36,960
Whoa, whoa, whoa, hold up. Hold up.
哇 哇 哇 等等 等等

1145
01:02:37,287 --> 01:02:38,391
Where are you all going?
你们要去哪?

1146
01:02:38,521 --> 01:02:40,589
- We're leaving.  - Really? What happened?
- 我们要走了  - 真的? 怎么回事?

1147
01:02:40,590 --> 01:02:42,524
- Adrian Keane was in that bar.  - Prick.
- 阿德里安・基恩在酒吧里  - 蠢货

1148
01:02:42,525 --> 01:02:44,026
I thought you liked Adrian Keane.
我还以为你喜欢阿德里安・基恩

1149
01:02:44,027 --> 01:02:45,728
- Adrian Keane is dead.  - Oh, God.
- 阿德里安・基恩已经死了  - 天啊

1150
01:02:45,729 --> 01:02:48,797
Adrian Keane died in a motorbike accident in Italy eight years ago.
八年前在意大利 阿德里安・基恩死于一场摩托车事故

1151
01:02:48,798 --> 01:02:50,666
- Did he?  - They must have had his DNA on file.
- 是吗?  - 他们肯定拿到了他的基因

1152
01:02:50,667 --> 01:02:52,010
That's how they were able to replicate him.
然后才能复制一个他

1153
01:02:52,202 --> 01:02:54,322
They know how to get to us, man. They know everything.
他们知道怎么抓到我们 老兄 他们知道一切

1154
01:02:54,471 --> 01:02:57,039
- They didn't know Adrian was dead.  - They knew enough to tempt us.
- 他们不知道阿德里安死了  - 他们知道的足够诱惑我们了

1155
01:02:57,040 --> 01:02:59,575
They knew these three would fall for a bunch of girls in school uniform.
他们知道这三个家伙看到穿着校服的姑娘就无法自拔

1156
01:02:59,576 --> 01:03:03,078
- Hey, who wouldn't? Am I right?  - Fuck, yeah.
- 嘿 谁不会呢? 我说的对吧?  - 他妈的还真对

1157
01:03:03,079 --> 01:03:04,213
We've gotta get out of town,
我们得离开这个镇子

1158
01:03:04,214 --> 01:03:05,625
we've gotta get beyond it before it's too late.
我们得在事情恶化之前离开这里

1159
01:03:05,882 --> 01:03:07,650
- Where are you getting all this from?  - Basil.
- 谁告诉你这些的?  - 巴希尔

1160
01:03:07,651 --> 01:03:10,953
Mad Basil? He of the Bermuda Rhombus and the Aqua Nazis?
疯子巴希尔? 说百慕大四角洲和水下纳粹的?

1161
01:03:10,954 --> 01:03:13,188
Another good name for the band, Steve.
又一个很好的乐队名字 史蒂文

1162
01:03:13,189 --> 01:03:15,024
You're putting our lives in the hands of a crazy old man?
你就把我们的生命赌在那个疯老头身上?

1163
01:03:15,025 --> 01:03:16,595
- He's not crazy!  - No, maybe he's not.
- 他没有疯!  - 或许他没疯

1164
01:03:16,760 --> 01:03:18,694
Or maybe he's a blank trying to lure us to the edge of town,
或许他就是个空壳人 想引诱我们走到镇子边缘的

1165
01:03:18,695 --> 01:03:21,196
onto those dark country roads where they can deal with us.
黑色乡间小路上 然后他们就会把我们干掉

1166
01:03:21,197 --> 01:03:24,566
- Yeah, we could end up dead in a field.  - I hate fields.
- 没错 我们可能最后会死在稻田里  - 我讨厌稻田

1167
01:03:24,567 --> 01:03:26,843
Yes. My thoughts precisely.
没错 我也是这么想的

1168
01:03:27,404 --> 01:03:29,405
Steven's right. We should go.
史蒂文说的对 我们应该离开

1169
01:03:29,406 --> 01:03:30,806
No, we're going to The Beehive.
不 我们要去蜂巢

1170
01:03:30,807 --> 01:03:32,309
Gary's plan is still the best we have.
加里的计划仍然是现在的最佳计划

1171
01:03:33,209 --> 01:03:34,187
Wait a minute
等一下

1172
01:03:36,680 --> 01:03:39,718
The 1990-model Oliver was out of commission by this point in the evening.
九零款奥利弗在今晚此时退役

1173
01:03:41,151 --> 01:03:42,152
What are you saying?
你在说什么?

1174
01:03:44,087 --> 01:03:46,288
- I like the new you.  - Huh.
- 我喜欢新的你  - 哈

1175
01:03:46,289 --> 01:03:47,267
Come on.
走吧

1176
01:03:48,792 --> 01:03:50,426
This is a mistake, isn't it?
这样做是不对的

1177
01:03:50,427 --> 01:03:51,748
Hold up! Just stick with me.
快点! 跟我走

1178
01:03:52,395 --> 01:03:53,533
Andy, come on!
安迪 来啊!

1179
01:03:55,465 --> 01:03:58,233
Here we go. Pub number nine.
到啦 第九个酒吧

1180
01:03:58,234 --> 01:03:59,268
Fuck yes!
太他妈对了!

1181
01:03:59,269 --> 01:04:01,749
That's the spirit, Pete! Spirits! We should do chasers.
这就是目标 目标! 皮特! 追求目标吧

1182
01:04:01,871 --> 01:04:03,238
Who is this guy?
你真令人刮目相看

1183
01:04:03,239 --> 01:04:06,686
Come on. Andy! It can't start without you.
来吧 安迪! 少了你就没法开始了

1184
01:04:09,346 --> 01:04:10,347
You what?
你说什么?

1185
01:04:10,847 --> 01:04:12,918
We can't start without you.
我们没你可不行

1186
01:04:17,454 --> 01:04:19,832
Now then. Whose round is it?
好 现在轮到谁了?

1187
01:04:20,123 --> 01:04:21,431
It's mine.
我来

1188
01:04:23,093 --> 01:04:24,902
Mr. Shepherd! Is it Mr. Shepherd?
谢菲尔德先生! 是谢菲尔德老师?

1189
01:04:25,195 --> 01:04:29,268
Why don't you kids join me? You look like you could do with a drink.
你们几个小鬼来一起坐吧? 一起喝一杯

1190
01:04:30,800 --> 01:04:35,806
Now, let's have a little chat about your future, shall we, hmm?
来谈谈你们的未来 怎么样?

1191
01:04:36,039 --> 01:04:39,282
- Uh, Mr. Shepherd?  - Please, call me Guy.
- 谢菲尔德老师?  - 请叫我哥们

1192
01:04:40,610 --> 01:04:41,588
All right.
好吧

1193
01:04:43,279 --> 01:04:44,280
Guy...
哥们...

1194
01:04:45,281 --> 01:04:46,692
Look at you.
瞧瞧你

1195
01:04:49,352 --> 01:04:50,422
Are you a robot?
你是机器人吗?

1196
01:04:51,121 --> 01:04:53,601
Does anyone know what robot means?
谁知道机器人语出何处?

1197
01:04:53,757 --> 01:04:54,929
- Yeah. I do!  - Yes, Gary.
- 我知道!  - 请说 加里

1198
01:04:55,358 --> 01:04:56,925
It means "slave."
意思就是"奴隶"

1199
01:04:56,926 --> 01:04:58,906
Oh, very good, Gary.
很好 加里

1200
01:04:59,396 --> 01:05:00,929
Are you a robot, sir?
那你是机器人吗?

1201
01:05:00,930 --> 01:05:03,843
No, Peter, of course I'm not a robot.
不 皮特 我当然不是

1202
01:05:03,967 --> 01:05:04,945
- Sir?  - Yes, Steven.
- 先生?  - 请说 史蒂文

1203
01:05:05,068 --> 01:05:06,468
But you're on their side, though?
但你站在他们那边的 对吗?

1204
01:05:06,469 --> 01:05:09,211
This is not about sides, Steven.
无关站在哪边 史蒂文

1205
01:05:09,372 --> 01:05:11,511
It's not about shirts versus skins.
这与外在无关

1206
01:05:11,641 --> 01:05:15,282
It's about working together as one team.
这关乎精诚合作

1207
01:05:15,445 --> 01:05:18,983
I know it may seem a bit weird and a little bit scary,
我知道有点奇怪 还有点吓人

1208
01:05:19,649 --> 01:05:21,788
but please believe me, it's quite the opposite,
当请相信我 完全不是这样的

1209
01:05:21,918 --> 01:05:23,552
They're here to help.
他们是来帮助我们的

1210
01:05:23,553 --> 01:05:27,000
To straighten us out. To prepare us for the big league.
纠正我们 让我们准备好加入大家庭

1211
01:05:27,357 --> 01:05:30,668
They've seen something in us, a potential.
他们能看到我们的潜力

1212
01:05:30,794 --> 01:05:33,331
There's a vast community of worlds up there,
在那上面还有个庞大的社会

1213
01:05:33,496 --> 01:05:37,706
living together, peacefully, cooperatively.
一起生活 和平 合作

1214
01:05:38,201 --> 01:05:41,205
And guess what? They want us along for the ride.
知道吗? 他们想让我们加入

1215
01:05:43,072 --> 01:05:45,245
Pretty cool, eh, gang?
很不错吧 兄弟们?

1216
01:05:45,375 --> 01:05:47,946
So, they're not here to harm us?
那么 他们不会伤害我们?

1217
01:05:48,344 --> 01:05:52,514
Far from it, O-Man. No, they're here to help.
怎么会呢 圈仔 他们是来提供帮助的

1218
01:05:52,515 --> 01:05:55,384
I'm not saying they're afraid to get tough.
我可没说他们惧怕暴力

1219
01:05:55,385 --> 01:05:58,127
I certainly had to get tough with you in my day.
过去我可被你们折腾的够呛

1220
01:05:58,521 --> 01:06:01,661
And what one amongst you wouldn't thank me for it? Hmm?
难道你们中没有一个人对我表示感谢吗?

1221
01:06:01,891 --> 01:06:05,227
In some respects, they're a lot like teachers.
请表示尊敬 他们其实更像教师

1222
01:06:05,228 --> 01:06:09,598
Stern, yes. A little frightening.
严格 没错 有些可怕

1223
01:06:09,599 --> 01:06:11,101
But it's all for our betterment.
但都是为了我们好

1224
01:06:12,035 --> 01:06:17,986
So, what do you say we all go somewhere and talk about this properly?
我们要不要一起换个地方体面地谈谈这事儿?

1225
01:06:18,241 --> 01:06:19,441
That wasn't properly?
这么谈不体面吗?

1226
01:06:19,442 --> 01:06:23,083
Well, I think it's pretty clear, guys, what Mr. Shepherd is trying to say is that...
嗯 我看很显然 谢菲尔德老师是想告诉我们...

1227
01:06:25,715 --> 01:06:28,025
Andy! What the fuck?
安迪! 你干什么?

1228
01:06:28,284 --> 01:06:30,730
Yes, Andy. What the fuck?
是啊 安迪 你干什么?

1229
01:06:35,391 --> 01:06:39,396
Humans, you leave us no recourse.
人类 你们让我们别无选择

1230
01:06:39,629 --> 01:06:42,610
If you will not join us willingly,
如果你们不肯自愿加入我们

1231
01:06:43,032 --> 01:06:47,069
we will be forced to use other means of persuasion.
我们只能采取别的方式让你们就范

1232
01:06:47,070 --> 01:06:48,708
Now, please...
现在 请...

1233
01:06:56,079 --> 01:06:57,956
I fucking hate this town!
我他妈恨死这里啦!

1234
01:07:38,588 --> 01:07:39,794
Oh, oh!
哦 哦!

1235
01:07:47,363 --> 01:07:49,240
- Oh, crumbs, you're heavy.  - Sorry.
- 哦 哥们 你真重  - 不好意思

1236
01:08:13,856 --> 01:08:15,164
Motherfucker!
该死的!

1237
01:08:34,911 --> 01:08:36,584
Andy!
安迪!

1238
01:08:36,813 --> 01:08:38,156
Twist the melon, man!
强扭瓜 哥们!

1239
01:08:40,950 --> 01:08:42,361
Yeah!
棒!

1240
01:08:44,454 --> 01:08:48,197
Sam, this is no way for a family to behave.
山姆 你难道连家人都不信任了吗

1241
01:08:56,966 --> 01:08:59,412
Sam, I'm disappointed in you.
山姆 我对你很失望

1242
01:09:05,842 --> 01:09:07,844
O-Man!
圈仔!

1243
01:09:22,558 --> 01:09:23,559
Okay, Andy.
好了 安迪

1244
01:09:23,926 --> 01:09:25,234
Break it up.
扯碎它

1245
01:09:26,929 --> 01:09:28,567
It doesn't have to be like this.
完全没必要这样

1246
01:09:29,766 --> 01:09:35,808
It could be so much simpler, so completely painless.
其实可以很简单的 完全没有痛苦的

1247
01:09:36,673 --> 01:09:38,840
If only you'd see the light.
你们只需要看着那光

1248
01:09:38,841 --> 01:09:40,075
Yes.
是的

1249
01:09:40,076 --> 01:09:43,683
See, it's not about conflict,
完全无需挣扎

1250
01:09:45,648 --> 01:09:47,449
it's about togetherness.
只是聚合而已

1251
01:09:47,450 --> 01:09:50,556
Yes. Let's try this again, shall we?
好吧 再来一波 怎么样?

1252
01:09:51,154 --> 01:09:52,155
How about another round?
在来一轮吧?

1253
01:09:52,722 --> 01:09:56,602
Nah, we're done here.
不了 这的酒已经喝了

1254
01:09:57,393 --> 01:10:01,029
Yes, Gary, that appears to be the case.
好吧 加里 那试试这个

1255
01:10:01,030 --> 01:10:02,441
The Smokehouse!
烟屋!

1256
01:10:02,932 --> 01:10:04,138
- What?  - Just do it!
- 什么?  - 快走!

1257
01:10:05,134 --> 01:10:06,112
Come on!
快点!

1258
01:10:07,036 --> 01:10:08,037
This way!
这边!

1259
01:10:18,014 --> 01:10:20,916
Humans, this is your final warning.
人类 这是最后通牒

1260
01:10:20,917 --> 01:10:23,193
Failure to comply will result in your...
若仍不服从 会导致...

1261
01:10:24,954 --> 01:10:28,424
Humans, obey now, or face the consequences.
人类 立即服从 否则将承担一切后果

1262
01:10:31,794 --> 01:10:32,795
Let's go!
快走!

1263
01:10:41,904 --> 01:10:43,042
Shit.
该死

1264
01:10:43,806 --> 01:10:45,012
Oh, look, there's my car!
哦 看 那是我的车!

1265
01:10:47,844 --> 01:10:49,084
Let's climb down the drainpipe.
顺着排水管下去

1266
01:10:50,246 --> 01:10:51,816
I've got a better idea.
我有更好的办法

1267
01:10:55,284 --> 01:10:56,763
Climb down the drainpipe.
还是爬水管吧

1268
01:11:00,590 --> 01:11:01,790
Okay, just go.
好了 快走

1269
01:11:01,791 --> 01:11:02,824
Wait. What about the others?
等等 他们呢?

1270
01:11:02,825 --> 01:11:04,392
Leave 'em with me, okay? I got this.
有我呢 交给我了

1271
01:11:04,393 --> 01:11:06,304
- Are you sure?  - Yeah, I always land on my feet.
- 你行吗?  - 当然 我绝对靠得住

1272
01:11:06,829 --> 01:11:08,150
I don't know if that's true, Gary.
让我很难相信 加里

1273
01:11:08,664 --> 01:11:09,665
Just go.
快走

1274
01:11:10,233 --> 01:11:12,034
Will you find out what happened to my brother?
别忘了找到我哥哥

1275
01:11:12,201 --> 01:11:15,705
Yeah, of course, of course, and I'll look after Stevie for you, eh?
当然 放心好了 我还会照顾好史蒂文的

1276
01:11:16,372 --> 01:11:19,046
He's a good guy. He's better than me.
他是个好男人 比我强

1277
01:11:19,776 --> 01:11:23,314
Gary, you're not a bad person, but you're not boyfriend material.
加里 你不是坏人 不过你不是当男朋友的料

1278
01:11:24,280 --> 01:11:27,082
